          <title>Vin&#237;cius J&#250;nior and Aitana Bonmati win FIFA best player of the year awards</title>
          <description><![CDATA[DOHA, Qatar (AP) — Real Madrid star Vinícius Júnior finally got his hands on a big global player award on Tuesday. Vinícius was named the men’s player of the year at the FIFA’s “The Best” awards, where Barcelona playmaker Aitana Bonmati continued to clean up in the prizes for women’s soccer.]]></description>
