          <title>Conor McGregor says he's in negotiations with Logan Paul for boxing exhibition in India</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Conor McGregor says he’s in negotiations to fight Logan Paul in a boxing exhibition in India. McGregor said early Tuesday morning on social media he’s in “preliminary agreements” with the family of billionaire industrialist Mukesh Ambani to fight Paul. “I have agreed,” McGregor said.]]></description>
